This project presents an **HR Analytics Dashboard** designed to analyze employee data and uncover insights related to **attrition, demographics, salary distribution, age, tenure, and job roles**. The dashboard helps HR teams and management make **dataâ€‘driven decisions** to improve employee retention and workforce planning.

